Package org.dmsextension.paperless.client.endpoints

Schnittstelle IParametrizedEndpoint

Alle Superschnittstellen:
IEndpoint
Alle bekannten Implementierungsklassen:
DocumentDownloadEndpoint, ParameterEndpoint, SingleCustomFieldEndpoint, SingleDocumentEndpoint, SingleStoragepathEndpoint
public interface IParametrizedEndpoint extends IEndpoint
Implemented by endpoint classes, that use a url with parameters. If, for example, the endpoint is /documents/{id}/update, the class has to implement this interface, in order to correctly build the url
